1-	LCN: 99900407
 Qarafi, Ahmad ibn Idris, Nafa'is al-usul fi sharh 
al-Mahsul / ta'lif Shihab al-Din Abi al-'Abbas Ahmad ibn 
Idris ibn 'Abd al-Rahman al-Sinhaji al-Misri al-ma'ruf 
bi-al-Qarafi ; i'dad Markaz al-Dirasat wa-al-Buhuth 
bi-Maktabat Nizar Mustafa al-Baz ; tahqiq 'Adil Ahmad 
'Abd al-Mawjud, 'Ali Muhammad Mu'awwad ; qarrazahu 'Abd 
al-Fattah Abu Sinnah. al-Tab'ah 2. Makkah : al-Maktabah, 
1997. $70.50 (U.S.) 9 v. (4320 p.) ; 25 cm. Commentary 
on al-Mahsul by al-Fakhr al-Razi; Islamic law; 
interpretation and construction; early works to 1800. 
 
 
